title: Don't Trend So Close To Me 2/4: MGT, AOC, "I Quit!", Chrissy Teigen, DJ Danl
itunes:title: Don't Trend So Close To Me 2/4: MGT, AOC, "I Quit!", Chrissy Teigen, DJ Danl
description:
On this edition of Don't Trend So Close To Me Jack and DJ Danl discuss the right/left push and pull of either getting MTG out of here or weirdly celebrating her. Republicans are claiming AOC's story is made up, Donald Trump quits SAG-AFTRA in a hilarious letter, Chrissy Teigen gets roasted for complaining about money, and DJ DANL GOT A PS5 WOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!
